<br>
He spawns just in front of the window and facing the bed, so hey, maybe if I sneak on the window sill he won't aggro me...  No such luck, there doesn't seem to be anywhere in that room where you can stand and not be attacked.  You just have to be able to grab the book and get out really fast, or be prepared for a fight.<br>
<br>
Fortunately, unlike all the other vampires, the servant doesn't lifetap, so he's hard, but not impossible for a mid-50s rogue to solo.  Although if he spawns with a long sword... <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><br><font color=#FF0000>- </font><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/bthesafehouse>The Safehouse</a><font color=#FF0000> - </font><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13>Quests of Norrath</a> <font color=#FF0000> - </font><a href="http://www.thesafehouse.org">The Safehouse website</a><font color=#FF0000> - </font> <center><a href="http://www.guildboss.com"><img
